                <title>mac查看端口占用情况</title>
                <description>&lt;h2 id=&quot;mac&quot;&gt;MAC下查看某个端口被哪个程序占用及杀进程方法&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;lsof&quot;&gt;lsof命令查看端口使用情况&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;通过list open file命令可以查看到当前打开文。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-&quot; data-lang=&quot;&quot;&gt;lsof -i:port
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;port替换成端口号，比如查看63342端口,使用如下&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-&quot; data-lang=&quot;&quot;&gt;lsof -i:63342
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;参数说明: -i表示网络链接,该命令会同时列出PID，方便kill&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-c&quot; data-lang=&quot;c&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;pengyouyideMacBook&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;Pro&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:~&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;pengyouyi&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;err&quot;&gt;$&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;lsof&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;i&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;63342&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;COMMAND&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;PID&lt;/span&gt;      &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;USER&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;FD&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;TYPE&lt;/span&gt;             &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;DEVICE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;SIZE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;OFF&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;NODE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;NAME&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;Google&lt;/span&gt;    &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;236&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;pengyouyi&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;93u&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;IPv4&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;mh&quot;&gt;0xe55f3646947d799f&lt;/span&gt;      &lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;t0&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;TCP&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;localhost&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;56933&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;localhost&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mi&quot;&gt;63342&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;ESTABLISHED&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
